{"tid":95670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有人約戰走數仲可以大條道理屈返人 係咩邏輯？","createTime":"2017-01-26T08:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:47:48.000Z","uid":319,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed88672c67125629e851b8211c51f634ca8eced","tid":95670,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁<br />\n有位「食魚有魚味」巴打<br />\n就好不滿一個會員「 Cowsep」<br />\n即係高登會員「勇武黑夜刺客」<br />\n佢經常喺政事台洗版 周圍屌人老母<br />\n然後就打算約佢出嚟<br />\n<br />\n誠意邀請cowsep巴打城下一聚 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/85785/page/9?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/85785/page/9?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n但呢個人之前已經有走數前科<br />\n喺高登果陣已經試過比人約戰走數<br />\n然後用一啲無理藉口話自己一早到左屈返人走數<br />\n所以咁多位巴打今次都叫樓主做好準備<br />\n唔好比「Cowsep」再用同一招走數<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0p76sY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0p76sY.jpg&h=8524b6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間就約左喺今朝11點HKU<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sy150yB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSy150yB.jpg&h=ba4f83e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161119_87f2649e5277ae8def075e0886abf591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161119_87f2649e5277ae8def075e0886abf591.jpg&h=6b72b412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主一直等到12點 「Cowsep」都無出現過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161247_2af0e368847e796f1196385a89ea4400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161247_2af0e368847e796f1196385a89ea4400.jpg&h=fb272659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15c0VuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15c0VuC.jpg&h=a7bb0f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161248_b9e0b9e1f226a28b3fee4a333d530dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161248_b9e0b9e1f226a28b3fee4a333d530dbb.jpg&h=7b308ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後幾個鐘後「Cowsep」上水<br />\n果然係用返同一招 屈返樓主遲到走數<br />\n<br />\n騙徒手法果然層出不窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f4beb02d400020cf5bb1aa83d5829b1c7c6440","tid":95670,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f919bcbb7c4465d844fad59ee14872c923ee0c0","tid":95670,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161815_8a0534a153ba442198979ec830d3f473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161815_8a0534a153ba442198979ec830d3f473.jpg&h=de4d9f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161816_8a0534a153ba442198979ec830d3f473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161816_8a0534a153ba442198979ec830d3f473.jpg&h=3d0428c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/161816_322e4870451efa9cf25e898ed435661d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F161816_322e4870451efa9cf25e898ed435661d.jpg&h=39ac925e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00841d31498bf97fb9fd58139cb3550e3f336ebc","tid":95670,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p